WEBVTT

00:00:00.310 --> 00:00:02.090

        MAJOR FUNDING 
        FOR THIS PROGRAM PROVIDED BY
      

00:00:02.090 --> 00:00:03.400

        THE FORD FOUNDATION,
       
      

00:00:03.400 --> 00:00:04.700

        A RESOURCE
        FOR INNOVATIVE PEOPLE
      

00:00:04.700 --> 00:00:06.670

        AND INSTITUTIONS WORLDWIDE,


00:00:06.670 --> 00:00:11.640

        AND THE CORPORATION
        FOR PUBLIC BROADCASTING.
      

00:00:11.640 --> 00:00:20.010

        ADDITIONAL FUNDING
        PROVIDED BY THESE FUNDERS --
      

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:55.220

        IT IS ALL AROUND US.


00:00:55.220 --> 00:00:58.890

        IT IS AN ILLUSION,
        AND YET PROFOUNDLY REAL.
      

00:00:58.890 --> 00:01:01.530

        WHAT WE PERCEIVE AS RACE


00:01:01.530 --> 00:01:05.200

        IS ONE OF THE FIRST THINGS
        WE NOTICE ABOUT EACH OTHER --
      

00:01:05.200 --> 00:01:08.230

        SKIN -- DARKER OR LIGHTER.


00:01:08.230 --> 00:01:11.070

        EYES -- ROUND OR ALMOND.


00:01:11.070 --> 00:01:15.840

        BLUE, BLACK, BROWN.


00:01:15.840 --> 00:01:18.310

        HAIR -- CURLY, STRAIGHT, BLONDE,


00:01:18.310 --> 00:01:21.510

        OR DARK.


00:01:21.510 --> 00:01:23.820

        AND ATTACHED
        TO THESE CHARACTERISTICS
      

00:01:23.820 --> 00:01:27.420

        IS A MOSAIC OF VALUES,
        ASSUMPTIONS,
      

00:01:27.420 --> 00:01:30.990

        AND HISTORICAL MEANINGS.


00:01:30.990 --> 00:01:35.190

        EVEN THOSE OF US WHO CLAIM
        WE DON'T BELIEVE THE STEREOTYPES
      

00:01:35.190 --> 00:01:37.960

        CAN EASILY RECITE THEM.


00:01:37.960 --> 00:01:42.470

        Man: THE AVERAGE PERSON
        ON THE STREET THINKS THAT RACE
      

00:01:42.470 --> 00:01:46.770

        CONSISTS OF DIFFERENCES
        IN PHYSICAL APPEARANCE.
      

00:01:46.770 --> 00:01:48.370

        THEY ALSO THINK


00:01:48.370 --> 00:01:50.510

        THAT FROM LOOKING AT
        A PERSON'S PHYSICAL APPEARANCE
      

00:01:50.510 --> 00:01:52.950

        THAT THEY CAN FIND OUT OR KNOW


00:01:52.950 --> 00:01:54.980

        MORE SUBTLE THINGS ABOUT THEM.


00:01:54.980 --> 00:01:58.890

        RACE IS NOT A LEVEL
        OF BIOLOGICAL DIVISION
      

00:01:58.890 --> 00:02:01.850

        THAT WE FIND
        IN ANATOMICALLY MODERN HUMANS.
      

00:02:01.850 --> 00:02:04.220

        THERE ARE NO SUBSPECIES


00:02:04.220 --> 00:02:08.960

        IN THE HUMAN BEINGS
        THAT LIVE TODAY.
      

00:02:08.960 --> 00:02:11.560

        AND THAT'S QUITE SHOCKING
        TO A LOT OF INDIVIDUALS.
      

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:14.630

        WHEN YOU LOOK
        AND YOU THINK YOU SEE RACE,
      

00:02:14.630 --> 00:02:17.270

        TO BE TOLD THAT NO,
        YOU DON'T SEE RACE,
      

00:02:17.270 --> 00:02:19.640

        YOU JUST THINK YOU SEE RACE,


00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:22.110

        THAT, YEAH, IT'S BASED
        ON YOUR CULTURAL LENS.
      

00:02:22.110 --> 00:02:25.840

        THAT'S EXTREMELY CHALLENGING.


00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:29.350

        Narrator: JUST BECAUSE RACE
        ISN'T A BIOLOGICAL REALITY,
      

00:02:29.350 --> 00:02:33.520

        DOESN'T MEAN IT ISN'T REAL.


00:02:33.520 --> 00:02:36.090

        BEING CLASSIFIED AS ASIAN


00:02:36.090 --> 00:02:38.890

        OR BLACK OR LATINO


00:02:38.890 --> 00:02:42.860

        HAS NEVER CARRIED THE SAME
        ADVANTAGES IN OUR SOCIETY
      

00:02:42.860 --> 00:02:46.600

        AS BEING WHITE.


00:02:46.600 --> 00:02:49.700

        Man: RACE IN ITSELF
        MEANS NOTHING.
      

00:02:49.700 --> 00:02:53.710

        THE MARKERS OF RACE --
        SKIN COLOR, HAIR TEXTURE,
      

00:02:53.710 --> 00:02:56.910

        THE THINGS THAT WE IDENTIFY
        AS THE RACIAL MARKERS
      

00:02:56.910 --> 00:03:00.810

        MEAN NOTHING, UNLESS THEY ARE
        GIVEN SOCIAL MEANING,
      

00:03:00.810 --> 00:03:03.950

        AND UNLESS THERE'S PUBLIC POLICY


00:03:03.950 --> 00:03:06.380

        AND PRIVATE ACTIONS


00:03:06.380 --> 00:03:10.190

        THAT ACT UPON
        THOSE KINDS OF CHARACTERISTICS.
      

00:03:10.190 --> 00:03:15.360

        THAT CREATES RACE.


00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:18.760

        Narrator: PHYSICAL DIFFERENCES
        DON'T MAKE RACE.
      

00:03:18.760 --> 00:03:22.000

        WHAT MAKES RACE
        ARE THE LAWS AND PRACTICES
      

00:03:22.000 --> 00:03:25.500

        THAT AFFECT LIFE CHANCES
        AND OPPORTUNITIES
      

00:03:25.500 --> 00:03:30.510

        BASED ON THOSE DIFFERENCES.


00:03:30.510 --> 00:03:31.880

        IF WE LOOK CAREFULLY,


00:03:31.880 --> 00:03:35.180

        WE CAN SEE HOW OUR INSTITUTIONS
        AND POLICIES
      

00:03:35.180 --> 00:03:37.520

        HAVE ASSIGNED RACIAL IDENTITIES


00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:39.390

        AND REINFORCED RACIAL INEQUALITY


00:03:39.390 --> 00:03:41.720

        THROUGHOUT THE 20th CENTURY.


00:03:41.720 --> 00:03:43.220

        Woman: AND THIS IS
        SOMETHING I THINK
      

00:03:43.220 --> 00:03:44.720

        THAT ALL IMMIGRANT GROUPS


00:03:44.720 --> 00:03:47.490

        EXPERIENCE IN ONE WAY OR ANOTHER
        WHEN THEY COME TO AMERICA,
      

00:03:47.490 --> 00:03:49.530

        NO MATTER
        WHAT POINT IN TIME IT IS.
      

00:03:49.530 --> 00:03:51.300

        BECAUSE THEY COME TO A COUNTRY


00:03:51.300 --> 00:03:55.770

        THAT HAS HISTORICALLY
        ALWAYS BEEN HIGHLY RACIALIZED.
      

00:03:55.770 --> 00:04:01.370

        IT'S A COUNTRY WHERE RACE
        HAS ITS ORIGINS IN SLAVERY
      

00:04:01.370 --> 00:04:06.810

        AS WELL AS IN THE CONQUEST
        OF NATIVE AMERICAN INDIANS.
      

00:04:06.810 --> 00:04:10.680

        SO, ANYBODY COMING FROM
        THE OUTSIDE AFTER THAT POINT
      

00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:14.490

        HAS TO FIT INTO THIS
        RACIALIZED SOCIETY IN SOME WAY.
      

00:04:14.490 --> 00:04:16.660

        AND IT'S NOT ALWAYS CLEAR


00:04:16.660 --> 00:04:26.470

        HOW PEOPLE ARE GOING
        TO FIT IN RIGHT AWAY.
      

00:04:26.470 --> 00:04:28.970

        Narrator: AT THE START
        OF THE 20th CENTURY,
      

00:04:28.970 --> 00:04:31.540

        AS MILLIONS OF IMMIGRANTS
        ARRIVED FROM ALL OVER THE WORLD,
      

00:04:31.540 --> 00:04:36.710

        LAWMAKERS AND SOCIAL
        SCIENTISTS DEBATED
      

00:04:36.710 --> 00:04:38.080

        HOW ALL OF THEM,


00:04:38.080 --> 00:04:40.780

        INCLUDING THE NEW
        EUROPEAN ARRIVALS,
      

00:04:40.780 --> 00:04:49.590

        WOULD FIT INTO THE HIERARCHY
        OF RACES ALREADY HERE.
      

00:04:49.590 --> 00:04:53.630

        THEY CAME SEEKING
        ECONOMIC OPPORTUNITY,
      

00:04:53.630 --> 00:05:03.900

        FREEDOM, AND A FUTURE
        FOR THEIR FAMILIES.
      

00:05:03.900 --> 00:05:08.840

        OF THE 23 MILLION NEWCOMERS
        BETWEEN 1880 AND 1920,
      

00:05:08.840 --> 00:05:24.620

        THE VAST MAJORITY WERE FROM
        EASTERN AND SOUTHERN EUROPE.
      

00:05:24.620 --> 00:05:26.930

        IMMIGRANTS OFTEN WORK
        THE HARDEST,
      

00:05:26.930 --> 00:05:29.760

        POOREST PAYING,
        AND MOST DANGEROUS JOBS,
      

00:05:29.760 --> 00:05:32.330

        ALONG WITH THE SO-CALLED


00:05:32.330 --> 00:05:35.400

        "INFERIOR RACES" ALREADY HERE --


00:05:35.400 --> 00:05:45.010

        BLACKS, MEXICANS, AND CHINESE.


00:05:45.010 --> 00:05:47.710

        Man: CITIES WITH
        ENORMOUS SLUMS DEVELOPED
      

00:05:47.710 --> 00:05:49.850

        AS THE UGLY SIDE


00:05:49.850 --> 00:05:52.450

        OF INDUSTRIALIZATION.


00:05:52.450 --> 00:05:54.220

        UGLY BOTH IN TERMS


00:05:54.220 --> 00:05:56.020

        OF THE AESTHETIC
        OF AMERICAN CITIES,
      

00:05:56.020 --> 00:05:58.690

        BUT ALSO UGLY IN TERMS OF
        THE SOLIDIFYING
      

00:05:58.690 --> 00:06:01.530

        OF CLASS DIFFERENCES
        AND CLASS TENSION.
      

00:06:01.530 --> 00:06:03.730

        AS ALL OF THOSE THINGS
        BECAME APPARENT,
      

00:06:03.730 --> 00:06:07.070

        THE IMMIGRANT BECAME THE SYMBOL


00:06:07.070 --> 00:06:11.640

        FOR WHAT AMERICA
        MIGHT BE BECOMING.
      

00:06:11.640 --> 00:06:13.410

        Narrator: BY 1910,


00:06:13.410 --> 00:06:16.840

        58% OF AMERICAN
        MINING AND FACTORY WORKERS
      

00:06:16.840 --> 00:06:20.850

        WERE IMMIGRANTS.


00:06:20.850 --> 00:06:23.950

        LIKE MEXICANS
        AND AFRICAN AMERICANS,
      

00:06:23.950 --> 00:06:25.620

        ITALIANS, SLAVS,


00:06:25.620 --> 00:06:28.420

        AND JEWS
        WERE OFTEN DESIRED AS LABORERS,
      

00:06:28.420 --> 00:06:30.820

        BUT ALSO FEARED,


00:06:30.820 --> 00:06:35.390

        SEEN AS PROMISCUOUS,
        LAZY, OR STUPID.
      

00:06:35.390 --> 00:06:40.670

        SOME SAW IT
        AS A RACIAL INVASION.
      

00:06:40.670 --> 00:06:43.840

        CHARLES DAVENPORT,
        A FAMOUS BIOLOGIST,
      

00:06:43.840 --> 00:06:49.040

        EXPRESSED THOSE FEARS IN 1911.


00:06:49.040 --> 00:06:51.740

        "THE POPULATION
        OF THE UNITED STATES,"
      

00:06:51.740 --> 00:06:54.080

        WROTE DAVENPORT,
        "WILL ON ACCOUNT
      

00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:58.020

        "OF THE GREAT INFLUX OF BLOOD
        FROM SOUTH EASTERN EUROPE,
      

00:06:58.020 --> 00:07:00.720

        "RAPIDLY BECOME
        DARKER IN PIGMENT,
      

00:07:00.720 --> 00:07:04.260

        "SMALLER IN STATURE,


00:07:04.260 --> 00:07:06.860

        "MORE GIVEN
        TO CRIMES OF LARCENY,
      

00:07:06.860 --> 00:07:09.930

        "KIDNAPPING, ASSAULT, MURDER,


00:07:09.930 --> 00:07:13.130

        "RAPE, AND SEXUAL IMMORALITY.


00:07:13.130 --> 00:07:16.900

        "AND THE RATIO OF INSANITY
        IN THE POPULATION
      

00:07:16.900 --> 00:07:19.340

        WILL RAPIDLY INCREASE."


00:07:19.340 --> 00:07:20.940

        Ngai:
        AND THIS WAS ALSO A TIME
      

00:07:20.940 --> 00:07:23.980

        WHEN SCIENTIFIC RACE THEORY
        BEGAN TO TAKE OFF,
      

00:07:23.980 --> 00:07:27.450

        AND PEOPLE BEGAN TO


00:07:27.450 --> 00:07:30.320

        LOOK AT SOCIETY,


00:07:30.320 --> 00:07:32.080

        AND LOOK AT GROUPS OF PEOPLE


00:07:32.080 --> 00:07:36.150

        IN MORE RACIALIZED TERMS.


00:07:36.150 --> 00:07:38.160

        SO, PEOPLE WERE PERCEIVED


00:07:38.160 --> 00:07:43.930

        AS BEING SEPARATE RACES.


00:07:43.930 --> 00:07:47.330

        SO YOU HAD KIND OF
        A HIGHER ORDER OF WHITE RACES,
      

00:07:47.330 --> 00:07:51.570

        YOU KNOW,
        WHICH WERE SEEN AS THE NORDICS,
      

00:07:51.570 --> 00:07:55.470

        AS OPPOSED TO WHAT
        MANY OF THE NATIVISTS CALLED
      

00:07:55.470 --> 00:08:01.950

        THE LOWER RACES OF EUROPE.


00:08:01.950 --> 00:08:03.450

        Jacobson:
        THERE ARE VARIOUS GROUPS
      

00:08:03.450 --> 00:08:05.220

        LIKE THE AMERICAN
        BREEDERS ASSOCIATION,
      

00:08:05.220 --> 00:08:07.120

        THE EUGENICS RESEARCH
        ASSOCIATION,
      

00:08:07.120 --> 00:08:10.860

        WHO NOT ONLY ARE DOING RESEARCH
        ON VARIOUS RACIAL TYPES,
      

00:08:10.860 --> 00:08:14.230

        IN THIS CASE HEBREWS, SLAVS,


00:08:14.230 --> 00:08:17.800

        MEDITERRANEANS.


00:08:17.800 --> 00:08:20.530

        WHAT WE WOULD CALL NOW
        THE CAUCASIAN RACE.
      

00:08:20.530 --> 00:08:21.970

        I WOULD BREAK IT DOWN


00:08:21.970 --> 00:08:26.810

        TO 35 OR 37
        OR 45 RACES FOR STUDY.
      

00:08:26.810 --> 00:08:30.810

        AND A LOT OF THE LANGUAGE WAS
        BEGINNING TO GET AT THE IDEA
      

00:08:30.810 --> 00:08:34.250

        THAT THOSE DIFFERENCES
        WERE ACTUALLY
      

00:08:34.250 --> 00:08:37.050

        ROOTED IN REPRODUCTION,


00:08:37.050 --> 00:08:39.080

        THEY WERE ROOTED
        IN INHERITABLE TRAITS,
      

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:40.850

        THEY WERE HERITABLE,


00:08:40.850 --> 00:08:45.160

        THEY WERE BIOLOGICAL,
        THEY WERE IMMUTABLE.
      

00:08:45.160 --> 00:08:46.930

        Narrator:
        THE MORE THE NEWCOMERS
      

00:08:46.930 --> 00:08:50.460

        WERE FORCED INTO LOW-PAYING JOBS
        AND DISEASED TENEMENTS,
      

00:08:50.460 --> 00:08:53.200

        THE MORE THESE CONDITIONS
        WERE EXPLAINED
      

00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:58.500

        AS NATURAL CONSEQUENCES OF
        THEIR INNATE RACIAL CHARACTER.
      

00:08:58.500 --> 00:09:02.170

        BIOLOGY WAS DESTINY.


00:09:02.170 --> 00:09:05.740

        WHICH SIDE OF THE RACIAL DIVIDE
        YOU FOUND YOURSELF ON
      

00:09:05.740 --> 00:09:09.480

        COULD BE A MATTER
        OF LIFE OR DEATH.
      

00:09:09.480 --> 00:09:12.750

        BETWEEN 1890 AND 1920,


00:09:12.750 --> 00:09:18.060

        2,500 AFRICAN AMERICANS
        WERE LYNCHED IN THE SOUTH.
      

00:09:18.060 --> 00:09:21.960

        IN 1915, LEO FRANK,


00:09:21.960 --> 00:09:25.130

        A JEW LIVING IN ATLANTA,


00:09:25.130 --> 00:09:28.500

        WAS PULLED FROM JAIL
        AND HANGED BY A MOB
      

00:09:28.500 --> 00:09:31.500

        FOR ALLEGEDLY
        KILLING A WHITE GIRL.
      

00:09:31.500 --> 00:09:34.470

        WRITING ABOUT THE LYNCHING,


00:09:34.470 --> 00:09:36.670

        A BLACK JOURNALIST WONDERED,


00:09:36.670 --> 00:09:41.650

        IS THE JEW A WHITE MAN?


00:09:41.650 --> 00:09:44.180

        Ngai: SOME HISTORIANS
        HAVE SUGGESTED THAT
      

00:09:44.180 --> 00:09:47.490

        THESE NEW IMMIGRANT GROUPS
        FROM EUROPE
      

00:09:47.490 --> 00:09:49.590

        WERE IN BETWEEN PEOPLES,


00:09:49.590 --> 00:09:51.760

        THEY WERE IN
        A TRANSITIONAL STAGE.
      

00:09:51.760 --> 00:09:54.830

        WHEN COMPARED TO


00:09:54.830 --> 00:09:56.500

        ANGLO-SAXON PROTESTANTS,


00:09:56.500 --> 00:09:59.700

        GROUPS SUCH AS ITALIANS OR JEWS


00:09:59.700 --> 00:10:03.470

        WERE SEEN AS NOT BEING
        FULLY WHITE PERHAPS.
      

00:10:03.470 --> 00:10:05.740

        BUT WHEN COMPARED
        TO AFRICAN AMERICANS
      

00:10:05.740 --> 00:10:07.970

        OR WHEN COMPARED TO ASIANS,


00:10:07.970 --> 00:10:09.970

        THEIR WHITENESS
        BECAME MORE SALIENT,
      

00:10:09.970 --> 00:10:13.980

        BECAME MORE VISIBLE.


00:10:13.980 --> 00:10:16.950

        Narrator: COULD EUROPEAN ETHNICS
        BECOME FULLY WHITE,
      

00:10:16.950 --> 00:10:19.280

        AND THUS, FULLY AMERICAN?


00:10:19.280 --> 00:10:24.290

        BY 1910, A NEW TERM
        WAS ENTERING POPULAR CULTURE
      

00:10:24.290 --> 00:10:28.390

        TO DESCRIBE
        THE TRANSFORMATION OF EUROPEANS.
      

00:10:28.390 --> 00:10:30.030

        THE PHRASE CAME FROM THE TITLE


00:10:30.030 --> 00:10:33.730

        OF A BROADWAY PLAY
        BY ISRAEL ZANGWILL.
      

00:10:33.730 --> 00:10:35.330

        "GOD," SAID ZANGWILL,


00:10:35.330 --> 00:10:37.400

        "WOULD MELT DOWN
        THE RACES OF EUROPE
      

00:10:37.400 --> 00:10:40.340

        "INTO A SINGLE PURE ESSENCE,


00:10:40.340 --> 00:10:44.810

        OUT OF WHICH
        HE WOULD MOLD AMERICANS."
      

00:10:44.810 --> 00:10:47.880

        Man: SO, WHEN THE IRISH,
        WHEN GERMANS,
      

00:10:47.880 --> 00:10:49.850

        WHEN ITALIANS WERE COMING


00:10:49.850 --> 00:10:51.480

        AND THEY DIDN'T
        SPEAK THE LANGUAGE
      

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:53.050

        AND THEY DIDN'T KNOW
        THE CULTURE,
      

00:10:53.050 --> 00:10:57.050

        THE IDEA WAS THEY WILL
        ASSIMILATE INTO AMERICAN-HOOD,
      

00:10:57.050 --> 00:10:59.290

        THEY WILL BECOME AMERICAN,


00:10:59.290 --> 00:11:01.360

        WHICH IN THE AMERICAN TRADITION
        HAS MEANT
      

00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:03.290

        WHITE AMERICAN.


00:11:03.290 --> 00:11:07.070

        BUT THAT MELTING POT
        NEVER INCLUDED PEOPLE OF COLOR.
      

00:11:07.070 --> 00:11:10.770

        BLACKS, CHINESE,
        PUERTO RICANS, ET CETERA,
      

00:11:10.770 --> 00:11:13.610

        COULD NOT MELT INTO THE POT.


00:11:13.610 --> 00:11:15.840

        THEY COULD BE USED AS WOOD


00:11:15.840 --> 00:11:18.180

        TO PRODUCE THE FIRE FOR THE POT,


00:11:18.180 --> 00:11:19.950

        BUT THEY COULD NOT BE USED


00:11:19.950 --> 00:11:24.350

        AS MATERIAL TO BE MELTED
        INTO THE POT.
      

00:11:24.350 --> 00:11:30.690

        Narrator: WHITENESS
        WAS KEY TO CITIZENSHIP.
      

00:11:30.690 --> 00:11:33.690

        IN 1790,
        CONGRESS HAD PASSED AN ACT
      

00:11:33.690 --> 00:11:36.700

        DECLARING THAT ONLY
        FREE WHITE IMMIGRANTS
      

00:11:36.700 --> 00:11:39.830

        COULD BECOME
        NATURALIZED CITIZENS.
      

00:11:39.830 --> 00:11:42.370

        AFTER THE CIVIL WAR,


00:11:42.370 --> 00:11:44.240

        NATURALIZATION WAS EXTENDED


00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:48.240

        TO PERSONS
        OF AFRICAN DESCENT AS WELL.
      

00:11:48.240 --> 00:11:50.410

        BUT IT WAS THE WHITE CITIZEN


00:11:50.410 --> 00:11:52.880

        WHO HAD CLEAR ACCESS
        TO THE VOTE,
      

00:11:52.880 --> 00:11:56.510

        SAT ON JURIES,
        WAS ELECTED TO PUBLIC OFFICE,
      

00:11:56.510 --> 00:11:58.420

        AND HAD BETTER JOBS.


00:11:58.420 --> 00:12:03.150

        WHITENESS WAS NOT SIMPLY
        A MATTER OF SKIN COLOR.
      

00:12:03.150 --> 00:12:07.130

        TO BE WHITE
        WAS TO GAIN THE FULL REWARDS
      

00:12:07.130 --> 00:12:11.000

        OF AMERICAN CITIZENSHIP.


00:12:11.000 --> 00:12:12.500

        Woman: IN ORDER TO BE


00:12:12.500 --> 00:12:14.430

        A NATURALIZED CITIZEN
        IN THIS COUNTRY,
      

00:12:14.430 --> 00:12:17.940

        YOU HAD TO BE CATEGORIZED
        AS WHITE OR BLACK,
      

00:12:17.940 --> 00:12:19.910

        AND ALMOST EVERYBODY
        WHO TRIED TO NATURALIZE,
      

00:12:19.910 --> 00:12:22.440

        ALL BUT I THINK ONE CASE
        THAT WENT TO THE SUPREME COURT,
      

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:25.680

        ALL OF THEM WERE PEOPLE TRYING
        TO BE CATEGORIZED AS WHITE.
      

00:12:25.680 --> 00:12:28.110

        SO THE COURT
        HAD TO MAKE DECISIONS ABOUT
      

00:12:28.110 --> 00:12:32.280

        WHO WAS WHITE AND WHO WAS NOT.


00:12:32.280 --> 00:12:35.020

        Narrator: COURTS AND LEGISLATORS
        HAD LONG BEEN IN THE BUSINESS
      

00:12:35.020 --> 00:12:37.690

        OF CONFERRING RACIAL IDENTITIES.


00:12:37.690 --> 00:12:41.030

        IN THE SOUTH, TO ENFORCE
        JIM CROW SEGREGATION
      

00:12:41.030 --> 00:12:43.660

        AND LAWS AGAINST
        MIXED MARRIAGES,
      

00:12:43.660 --> 00:12:45.900

        COURTS HAD TO FIRST DETERMINE


00:12:45.900 --> 00:12:48.700

        WHO WAS BLACK UNDER LAW.


00:12:48.700 --> 00:12:51.200

        Man: AND HERE IS WHERE
        IT REALLY GETS INTERESTING.
      

00:12:51.200 --> 00:12:54.640

        YOU GOT SOME PLACES,
        FOR EXAMPLE, VIRGINIA.
      

00:12:54.640 --> 00:12:57.740

        VIRGINIA LAW
        DEFINED A BLACK PERSON
      

00:12:57.740 --> 00:13:01.510

        AS A PERSON
        WITH 1/16th AFRICAN ANCESTRY.
      

00:13:01.510 --> 00:13:04.050

        NOW, FLORIDA DEFINED
        A BLACK PERSON
      

00:13:04.050 --> 00:13:08.420

        AS A PERSON
        WITH 1/8th AFRICAN ANCESTRY.
      

00:13:08.420 --> 00:13:11.660

        ALABAMA SAID YOU'RE BLACK
        IF YOU GOT ANY BLACK ANCESTRY,
      

00:13:11.660 --> 00:13:13.430

        ANY AFRICAN ANCESTRY AT ALL.


00:13:13.430 --> 00:13:15.690

        BUT YOU KNOW WHAT THIS MEANS?


00:13:15.690 --> 00:13:17.830

        YOU CAN WALK ACROSS A STATE LINE


00:13:17.830 --> 00:13:21.200

        AND LITERALLY,
        LEGALLY, CHANGE RACE.
      

00:13:21.200 --> 00:13:24.670

        NOW, WHAT DOES RACE MEAN
        UNDER THOSE CIRCUMSTANCES?
      

00:13:24.670 --> 00:13:26.170

        YOU GIVE ME THE POWER,


00:13:26.170 --> 00:13:28.510

        I CAN MAKE YOU
        ANY RACE I WANT YOU TO BE,
      

00:13:28.510 --> 00:13:35.010

        BECAUSE IT IS
        A SOCIAL POLITICAL CONSTRUCTION.
      

00:13:35.010 --> 00:13:39.350

        Narrator: IN 1909,
        AMERICAN COURTS HAD THAT POWER.
      

00:13:39.350 --> 00:13:43.360

        THAT YEAR, THE U.S. COURT
        OF APPEALS IN MASSACHUSETTS
      

00:13:43.360 --> 00:13:45.160

        RULED THAT ARMENIANS,


00:13:45.160 --> 00:13:47.830

        OFTEN CLASSIFIED
        AS ASIATIC TURKS,
      

00:13:47.830 --> 00:13:51.030

        WERE LEGALLY WHITE.


00:13:51.030 --> 00:13:54.800

        IF ARMENIANS
        COULD BE DESIGNATED WHITE,
      

00:13:54.800 --> 00:13:58.800

        WHAT OF THE OTHER
        SO-CALLED ASIATIC RACES?
      

00:13:58.800 --> 00:14:01.040

        FILIPINOS,


00:14:01.040 --> 00:14:03.510

        SYRIANS,


00:14:03.510 --> 00:14:06.810

        THE JAPANESE?


00:14:06.810 --> 00:14:09.350

        COULD THEY ALSO
        PETITION SUCCESSFULLY
      

00:14:09.350 --> 00:14:12.480

        TO BE DESIGNATED WHITE
        BY THE COURTS,
      

00:14:12.480 --> 00:14:22.330

        AND THUS BECOME AMERICANS?


00:14:22.330 --> 00:14:27.170

        IN 1922, WHEN JAPANESE
        BUSINESSMAN TAKAO OZAWA
      

00:14:27.170 --> 00:14:30.470

        PETITIONED THE SUPREME COURT
        FOR NATURALIZATION,
      

00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:32.670

        MANY IN THE JAPANESE COMMUNITY


00:14:32.670 --> 00:14:36.510

        BELIEVED HIS
        WAS THE PERFECT TEST CASE.
      

00:14:36.510 --> 00:14:40.150

        Ngai:
        TAKAO OZAWA CAME FROM JAPAN,
      

00:14:40.150 --> 00:14:42.080

        WENT TO THE UNIVERSITY
        OF CALIFORNIA AT BERKELEY
      

00:14:42.080 --> 00:14:44.150

        FOR A FEW YEARS,


00:14:44.150 --> 00:14:47.420

        THEN MOVED TO HAWAII
        WHERE HE HAD A FAMILY,
      

00:14:47.420 --> 00:14:49.490

        AND HE APPLIED


00:14:49.490 --> 00:14:53.530

        TO BECOME
        A NATURALIZED CITIZEN IN 1915.
      

00:14:53.530 --> 00:14:57.400

        Woman: MY FATHER WROTE
        HIS OWN BRIEF AND EVERYTHING,
      

00:14:57.400 --> 00:15:00.730

        AND HE WAS REALLY DEVOTED,


00:15:00.730 --> 00:15:03.930

        HE WANTED TO BECOME
        AN AMERICAN CITIZEN.
      

00:15:03.930 --> 00:15:08.470

        AND NOTHING WOULD STOP HIM.


00:15:08.470 --> 00:15:12.380

        HE WAS DETERMINED.


00:15:12.380 --> 00:15:14.650

        Narrator:
        JAPANESE GROWERS IN CALIFORNIA
      

00:15:14.650 --> 00:15:17.850

        WATCHED OZAWA'S CASE CLOSELY.


00:15:17.850 --> 00:15:21.850

        BY 1920, A SERIES
        OF ALIEN LAND ACTS
      

00:15:21.850 --> 00:15:24.220

        PROHIBITED MANY NON-CITIZENS


00:15:24.220 --> 00:15:27.030

        FROM OWNING OR LEASING LAND.


00:15:27.030 --> 00:15:29.830

        WITHOUT A LEGAL DESIGNATION
        OF WHITENESS
      

00:15:29.830 --> 00:15:31.730

        TO MAKE THEM CITIZENS,


00:15:31.730 --> 00:15:33.600

        JAPANESE IMMIGRANTS
        COULD NOT HAVE
      

00:15:33.600 --> 00:15:36.200

        THE FULL PROTECTION
        OF AMERICAN LAW,
      

00:15:36.200 --> 00:15:40.340

        NO MATTER HOW LONG
        THEY LIVED IN THE COUNTY.
      

00:15:40.340 --> 00:15:45.580

        IN HIS BRIEF,
        OZAWA ARGUED THAT HIS SKIN
      

00:15:45.580 --> 00:15:48.080

        WAS AS WHITE
        AS ANY SO-CALLED CAUCASIAN,
      

00:15:48.080 --> 00:15:49.980

        IF NOT WHITER.


00:15:49.980 --> 00:15:53.590

        BUT HE MADE A MUCH MORE
        IMPORTANT SECOND ARGUMENT.
      

00:15:53.590 --> 00:15:55.420

        BUT HIS SECOND ARGUMENT WAS


00:15:55.420 --> 00:15:58.690

        THAT RACE SHOULDN'T MATTER
        FOR CITIZENSHIP.
      

00:15:58.690 --> 00:16:03.290

        WHAT REALLY MATTERED
        WAS A PERSON'S BELIEFS.
      

00:16:03.290 --> 00:16:05.630

        Narrator:
        "MY HONESTY AND INDUSTRIOUSNESS
      

00:16:05.630 --> 00:16:07.130

        "ARE WELL KNOWN AMONG


00:16:07.130 --> 00:16:10.300

        "MY JAPANESE
        AND AMERICAN FRIENDS.
      

00:16:10.300 --> 00:16:14.010

        "IN NAME,
        BENEDICT ARNOLD WAS AN AMERICAN,
      

00:16:14.010 --> 00:16:16.310

        "BUT AT HEART HE WAS A TRAITOR.


00:16:16.310 --> 00:16:19.880

        "IN NAME, I AM NOT AN AMERICAN,


00:16:19.880 --> 00:16:21.810

        "BUT AT HEART,


00:16:21.810 --> 00:16:25.320

        I AM A TRUE AMERICAN."


00:16:25.320 --> 00:16:28.290

        THE ARTICLES
        WOULD COME OUT IN THE PAPER.
      

00:16:28.290 --> 00:16:32.320

        I THOUGHT, OOH,
        WHAT DID HE DO, YOU KNOW?
      

00:16:32.320 --> 00:16:36.090

        I THOUGHT ONLY BAD THINGS
        CAME OUT IN THE PAPER,
      

00:16:36.090 --> 00:16:38.430

        AND I WAS KIND OF ASHAMED,
        YOU KNOW,
      

00:16:38.430 --> 00:16:41.000

        WHEN I WAS A CHILD.


00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:44.000

        AND IT WAS JUST THE WAY


00:16:44.000 --> 00:16:46.200

        WE WERE BROUGHT UP.


00:16:46.200 --> 00:16:49.010

        I DIDN'T HAVE
        ANY ORIENTAL FRIENDS.
      

00:16:49.010 --> 00:16:52.810

        MY NEIGHBORS WERE ALL CAUCASIAN,


00:16:52.810 --> 00:16:56.650

        AND SO HE WAS SO DETERMINED
        TO GET US --
      

00:16:56.650 --> 00:17:03.890

        WELL, WHEN THE TIME CAME,
        TO BE AMERICAN CITIZENS.
      

00:17:03.890 --> 00:17:06.190

        Ngai: THE SUPREME COURT


00:17:06.190 --> 00:17:09.630

        RULED THAT OZAWA
        COULD NOT BE A CITIZEN.
      

00:17:09.630 --> 00:17:11.130

        THEY SAID HE WAS NOT WHITE


00:17:11.130 --> 00:17:12.700

        WITHIN THE MEANING
        OF THE STATUTE,
      

00:17:12.700 --> 00:17:16.100

        AND THEREFORE
        NOT ELIGIBLE TO CITIZENSHIP.
      

00:17:16.100 --> 00:17:17.840

        AND THE COURT SAID,


00:17:17.840 --> 00:17:20.670

        WELL, HE'S NOT WHITE
        BECAUSE HE'S NOT CAUCASIAN,
      

00:17:20.670 --> 00:17:23.540

        AND CAUCASIANS ARE WHITES.


00:17:23.540 --> 00:17:25.940

        HE DID EVERYTHING RIGHT.


00:17:25.940 --> 00:17:28.180

        HE LEARNED ENGLISH.


00:17:28.180 --> 00:17:32.050

        HE HAD A LIFESTYLE
        THAT WAS AMERICAN.
      

00:17:32.050 --> 00:17:34.650

        HE WENT TO
        CHRISTIAN CHURCH ON SUNDAY,
      

00:17:34.650 --> 00:17:37.160

        HE DRESSED AS A WESTERNER,


00:17:37.160 --> 00:17:40.990

        HE BROUGHT UP HIS CHILDREN
        AS AMERICANS.
      

00:17:40.990 --> 00:17:42.860

        HE DID EVERYTHING
        HE WAS SUPPOSED TO DO,
      

00:17:42.860 --> 00:17:46.330

        AND YET HE'S TOLD
        THAT HE CAN'T BE A CITIZEN
      

00:17:46.330 --> 00:17:50.170

        BECAUSE HE'S NOT WHITE.


00:17:50.170 --> 00:17:51.440

        Narrator: THE COURT RULED


00:17:51.440 --> 00:17:53.970

        THAT ACCORDING TO
        THE BEST KNOWN SCIENCE,
      

00:17:53.970 --> 00:17:56.580

        OZAWA WAS NOT CAUCASIAN,


00:17:56.580 --> 00:17:59.680

        BUT OF THE MONGOLIAN RACE.


00:17:59.680 --> 00:18:02.250

        BUT THE COURT WOULD NOT
        BE BOUND BY SCIENCE
      

00:18:02.250 --> 00:18:07.050

        IN POLICING
        THE BOUNDARIES OF WHITENESS.
      

00:18:07.050 --> 00:18:09.420

        ONLY THREE MONTHS AFTER OZAWA,


00:18:09.420 --> 00:18:12.790

        THE COURT TOOK UP THE CASE
        OF BHAGAT SINGH THIND,
      

00:18:12.790 --> 00:18:15.790

        A SOUTH ASIAN IMMIGRANT
        AND U.S. ARMY VETERAN
      

00:18:15.790 --> 00:18:18.360

        WHO PETITIONED FOR CITIZENSHIP
        ON THE GROUNDS
      

00:18:18.360 --> 00:18:22.130

        THAT INDIANS WERE OF
        THE ARYAN OR CAUCASIAN RACE,
      

00:18:22.130 --> 00:18:24.600

        AND THEREFORE WHITE.


00:18:24.600 --> 00:18:27.310

        AND HE MAKES
        THE SCIENTIFIC ARGUMENT,
      

00:18:27.310 --> 00:18:30.410

        HAVING LEARNED SOMETHING,
        ACTUALLY, FROM THE OZAWA CASE,
      

00:18:30.410 --> 00:18:32.010

        THAT HE IS CAUCASIAN.


00:18:32.010 --> 00:18:34.810

        HE GETS SCIENTIFIC AUTHORITY
        TO SPEAK ON HIS BEHALF,
      

00:18:34.810 --> 00:18:39.180

        THAT IN FACT, SOUTH ASIANS ARE
        INCLUDED IN THE CAUCASIAN RACE.
      

00:18:39.180 --> 00:18:40.890

        Ngai: SO HERE THE COURT
        WAS IN A BIND,
      

00:18:40.890 --> 00:18:42.990

        BECAUSE THEY WERE PRESENTED WITH


00:18:42.990 --> 00:18:45.860

        SO-CALLED SCIENTIFIC EVIDENCE


00:18:45.860 --> 00:18:50.490

        THAT INDIANS WERE CAUCASIAN.


00:18:50.490 --> 00:18:54.030

        AND THE COURT
        SOLVED THIS PROBLEM BY SAYING
      

00:18:54.030 --> 00:18:58.970

        THAT IT DIDN'T MATTER WHAT
        SCIENCE SAID, SO-CALLED SCIENCE.
      

00:18:58.970 --> 00:19:01.810

        THEY ACTUALLY SAID,


00:19:01.810 --> 00:19:04.840

        WHITE IS NOT SOMETHING THAT CAN
        BE SCIENTIFICALLY DETERMINED,
      

00:19:04.840 --> 00:19:08.680

        BUT WHITE IS SOMETHING THAT IS
        SUBJECTIVELY UNDERSTOOD
      

00:19:08.680 --> 00:19:11.420

        BY WHO THEY CALLED
        THE COMMON PERSON,
      

00:19:11.420 --> 00:19:15.650

        THE COMMON MAN.


00:19:15.650 --> 00:19:18.190

        Narrator: "IT MAY BE TRUE,"
        REASONED THE COURT,
      

00:19:18.190 --> 00:19:21.130

        "THAT THE BLONDE SCANDINAVIAN
        AND THE BROWN HINDU
      

00:19:21.130 --> 00:19:25.300

        "HAVE A COMMON ANCESTOR IN
        THE DIM REACHES OF ANTIQUITY,
      

00:19:25.300 --> 00:19:28.200

        "BUT THE AVERAGE MAN
        KNOWS PERFECTLY WELL
      

00:19:28.200 --> 00:19:31.970

        "THAT THERE ARE UNMISTAKABLE
        AND PROFOUND DIFFERENCES
      

00:19:31.970 --> 00:19:36.040

        BETWEEN THEM TODAY."


00:19:36.040 --> 00:19:38.310

        THE SAME COURT THAT USED SCIENCE


00:19:38.310 --> 00:19:42.310

        TO DETERMINE WHITENESS IN OZAWA
        THREE MONTHS BEFORE,
      

00:19:42.310 --> 00:19:46.150

        NOW REFUTED
        ITS OWN REASONING IN THIND.
      

00:19:46.150 --> 00:19:50.820

        THIND MIGHT WELL BE CAUCASIAN,
        THE HIGH COURT SAID,
      

00:19:50.820 --> 00:19:53.490

        BUT HE WAS NOT WHITE.


00:19:53.490 --> 00:19:56.690

        THE JUSTICES NEVER SAID
        WHAT WHITENESS WAS,
      

00:19:56.690 --> 00:19:58.360

        ONLY WHAT IT WASN'T.


00:19:58.360 --> 00:20:01.230

        THEIR IMPLIED LOGIC
        WAS A CIRCULAR ONE.
      

00:20:01.230 --> 00:20:02.900

        WHITENESS WAS


00:20:02.900 --> 00:20:06.240

        WHAT THE COMMON WHITE MAN
        SAID IT WAS.
      

00:20:06.240 --> 00:20:09.270

        Ossorio: THE COURT OFTEN DECIDED
        WHO WAS WHITE AND WHO WASN'T
      

00:20:09.270 --> 00:20:11.410

        BASED ON WHETHER THEY FELT
        THAT THE PERSON
      

00:20:11.410 --> 00:20:14.480

        WOULD POLITICALLY FIT WELL
        INTO THE KIND OF SOCIETY
      

00:20:14.480 --> 00:20:15.650

        THAT WE WERE TRYING TO BUILD.


00:20:15.650 --> 00:20:17.620

        AND SOMETIMES IT WAS
        PRETTY EXPLICIT
      

00:20:17.620 --> 00:20:19.250

        THAT THIS IS WHAT
        THE COURT WAS DOING.
      

00:20:19.250 --> 00:20:22.090

        THERE WAS WIDESPREAD
        RACIAL VIEWS
      

00:20:22.090 --> 00:20:24.260

        THAT ASIANS WERE UNDESIRABLE,


00:20:24.260 --> 00:20:26.860

        THAT THEY THREATENED


00:20:26.860 --> 00:20:31.730

        TO CONTAMINATE
        THE AMERICAN SOCIETY.
      

00:20:31.730 --> 00:20:33.870

        BASICALLY THAT ASIANS
        ARE TOO DIFFERENT,
      

00:20:33.870 --> 00:20:44.340

        THAT THEY CAN'T EVER REALLY
        BECOME LIKE THE REST OF US.
      

00:20:44.340 --> 00:20:46.780

        Narrator: THE CONSEQUENCES
        OF THE UNANIMOUS VERDICT
      

00:20:46.780 --> 00:20:48.550

        IN U.S. v THIND


00:20:48.550 --> 00:20:51.550

        WERE CATASTROPHIC
        FOR THE INDIAN COMMUNITY.
      

00:20:51.550 --> 00:20:55.150

        SOUTH ASIANS WHO HAD NATURALIZED
        BEFORE THE VERDICT
      

00:20:55.150 --> 00:21:01.460

        WERE STRIPPED OF THEIR
        CITIZENSHIP AND PROPERTY.
      

00:21:01.460 --> 00:21:04.490

        VAISHO DAS BAGAI
        WAS A SUCCESSFUL MERCHANT
      

00:21:04.490 --> 00:21:06.600

        WHO FLED
        BRITISH TYRANNY IN INDIA
      

00:21:06.600 --> 00:21:11.500

        TO RAISE HIS FAMILY
        IN A FREE COUNTRY.
      

00:21:11.500 --> 00:21:15.340

        AFTER HIS AMERICAN CITIZENSHIP
        WAS REVOKED,
      

00:21:15.340 --> 00:21:18.280

        HE TOOK HIS OWN LIFE.


00:21:18.280 --> 00:21:20.740

        HE LEFT A SUICIDE NOTE
        FOR HIS FAMILY
      

00:21:20.740 --> 00:21:24.620

        AND ANOTHER FOR THE PUBLIC.


00:21:24.620 --> 00:21:26.880

        "BUT NOW THEY COME AND SAY TO ME


00:21:26.880 --> 00:21:29.690

        "I AM NO LONGER
        AN AMERICAN CITIZEN.
      

00:21:29.690 --> 00:21:33.360

        "WHAT HAVE I MADE OF MYSELF
        AND MY CHILDREN?
      

00:21:33.360 --> 00:21:35.860

        "WE CANNOT EXERCISE OUR RIGHTS,


00:21:35.860 --> 00:21:38.190

        "WE CANNOT LEAVE THIS COUNTRY.


00:21:38.190 --> 00:21:40.700

        "HUMILITY AND INSULTS,


00:21:40.700 --> 00:21:42.530

        "BLOCKADES THIS WAY,


00:21:42.530 --> 00:22:01.490

        AND BRIDGES BURNED BEHIND."


00:22:01.490 --> 00:22:03.390

        FOR THE JAPANESE COMMUNITY,


00:22:03.390 --> 00:22:05.590

        THE VERDICTS IN THE OZAWA
        AND THIND CASES
      

00:22:05.590 --> 00:22:10.290

        WERE EQUALLY DEVASTATING.


00:22:10.290 --> 00:22:14.970

        NOW, AS ALIENS
        INELIGIBLE FOR CITIZENSHIP,
      

00:22:14.970 --> 00:22:18.840

        MANY GROWERS WERE UNABLE
        TO PURCHASE OR EVEN LEASE LAND
      

00:22:18.840 --> 00:22:20.570

        TO STAY IN BUSINESS.


00:22:20.570 --> 00:22:22.670

        THOUSANDS OF ACRES WERE SEIZED


00:22:22.670 --> 00:22:24.510

        FROM JAPANESE IMMIGRANTS


00:22:24.510 --> 00:22:27.850

        AND SOLD TO WHITE FARMERS.


00:22:27.850 --> 00:22:30.180

        BY THE TIME
        THE RACIAL REQUIREMENT
      

00:22:30.180 --> 00:22:34.080

        FOR NATURALIZATION
        WAS FINALLY REMOVED IN 1952,
      

00:22:34.080 --> 00:22:38.520

        TAKAO OZAWA WAS LONG DEAD.


00:22:38.520 --> 00:22:42.360

        Ngai: THE NOTION THAT ASIANS
        ARE RACIALLY UNASSIMILABLE,
      

00:22:42.360 --> 00:22:44.360

        AND THAT THEY'RE
        INELIGIBLE TO CITIZENSHIP
      

00:22:44.360 --> 00:22:47.030

        BECAUSE OF THEIR RACE


