00:23:07.050 --> 00:23:09.150

        AND TO PUT THEM
        IN INTERNMENT CAMPS
      

00:23:09.150 --> 00:23:12.160

        DURING WORLD WAR II.


00:23:12.160 --> 00:23:17.490

        THE LEGACY OF THIS IDEA
